CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

November 20, 2007

[Cite as 11/20/2007 Case Announcements, 2007-Ohio-6173.]

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2006-2406. Thompson v. Jones-Kelley.

Franklin App. No. 05AP-476, 2006-Ohio-6000. On motion to dismiss the appeal as moot. Motion granted. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., and O’Donnell, Lanzinger, and Cupp, JJ., concur. Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, and O’Connor, JJ., dissent.
